Cell.Text: It's all over! Everything is ruined! | Cap’n! Please! Ya gotta help me! My engagement ring is gone!

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2HelpTretTopic: Hey you look worried, are you okay?

Cell.Text: G|Good luck with that! I've tried me hardest, but the lot of 'em have just driven me to another bottle o'rum!

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2GetToTheBottom: I'll get to the bottom of this!

Cell.Text: [S] Aye, he asked me to look into it, so I 'ave, and It looks like we have thief in our midst! I've narrowed it down to four people. | Hook, Jones, Davy, and Barbaros, 'tis definitely one of 'em! And I know for a fact that only one of them is telling the truth... | But the rest are rotten liars!

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2JoshameeAskTopic: Hey Gibbs, you know anything about Tret's missing ring?

Cell.Text: Well... Joshamee was also looking into it for me, maybe he knows something by now.

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2WhoToAskTopic: Know anything that will help me find it?

Cell.Text: Davy stole it! I saw him do it!
I think Hook stole the ring.
I dunno, but I reckon Hook is a rotten lier!
Well, I didn't steal anything if that’s what yer askin’.
[S] G|What? I didn't steal the ring! How dare you! I'm as honest as they come!
[S] G|I did no such thing! How dare you!
[S] G|You what matey? 'ow dare you! I'd never do such a thing!
[S] G|Blast it! You got me... If it weren't for those meddling kids I would have gotten away with it! Here, take it!

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2AccuseTopic: I think you stole the ring!

Cell.Text: [S] You found it?! By the seven seas cap'n, I'm in your debt! Thank you so much!

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2GiveRingTopic: Great news! I found your ring, here.

Cell.Text: [S] What? No! This is just awful! She'll never marry me now! My life is ruined!
[S] What? No! This is just awful! She'll never marry me now...

Node.Caption: LASCrewmateQuest2NotGiveRingTopic: I'm sorry but I couldn't find your ring...

Cell.Text: G|Hey cap'n! I just wanted ya to know I really appreciate all yer work for me.
G|Please, I just want to be left alone right now...
